Title: Amazing, lncredible, Historical Portugal Treasures
DateModified: '2019-03-12'
DatePublished: '2019-03-12'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/amazing-lncredible-historical-portugal-treasures
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Liz Meisekothen
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Portugal brings to life culture, discoveries, adventure, faith, culinary delights,\
  \ hidden gems, diversity, and breathe taking scenery.\n     One untapped jewel,\
  \ not discovered by the travel market, are the Portuguese Azores.  Come to the Azores!\
  \  See the whales, dolphins, and turtles.  Hit the uncrowded beaches!  Relax.  Rare\
  \ beauty awaits in the dorment volcanoes.\n     Treat yourself to a pineapple drink\
  \ and incredible wines rivaling the best.  Enjoy fresh seafood and European delights.\
  \ \n      Adventure on some of the most incredible hikes in the world.  Or simply\
  \ stroll down well designed volcanic and stone sidewalk.  Stop at a cafe or bakery.\
  \  Culinary arts at its finest.  The best of Europe.  World Class.  Easy to access\
  \ by air or by sea.  The best of modern life and European charm.  You will want\
  \ more.  It will be one of your most memorable vacations."
